OL,3,CA303 closed westbound after multi-
OL,4,Cvehicle collision
OL,6,FA section of the westbound A303 has
OL,7,Fbeen closed for resurfacing work after
OL,8,Fthree people were injured in a multi-
OL,9,Fvehicle collision.
OL,11,FEmergency services and the air
OL,12,Fambulance were called at 12.30 on
OL,13,FSaturday April 11th after four
OL,14,Fvehicles- a Vauxhall Mokka, a Ford
OL,15,FPuma, a Ford Kuga and a Volvo `
OL,16,Fcollided between the junctions of
OL,17,FThruxton Circuit and Salisbury Road.
OL,19,FThe driver of the Vauxhall, an
OL,20,F82yearold woman, sustained serious,
OL,21,Fpotentially lifethreatening injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
