OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776041694
OL,3,CA303 closed westbound after multi-
OL,4,Cvehicle collision
OL,6,FThe passenger of the Vauxhall, a
OL,7,F78yearold man, suffered injuries to
OL,8,Fhis chest which are not believed to be
OL,9,Flifethreatening or lifechanging.
OL,11,FThey remain in hospital receiving
OL,12,Ftreatment.
OL,14,FA passenger of the Volvo, a 9-year-old
OL,15,Fgirl, also suffered minor injuries.
OL,17,FHampshire Police are investigating the
OL,18,Fincident, and are appealing for anyone
OL,19,Fwho witnessed the collision, the
OL,20,Fmoments leading up to it, or the
OL,21,Fimmediate aftermath.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
