OL,3,CA303 closed westbound after multi-
OL,4,Cvehicle collision
OL,6,FMotorists were trapped for several
OL,7,Fhours yesterday as emergency services
OL,8,Fattended the scene.
OL,10,FNational Highways said the carriageway
OL,11,Fhad suffered serious damage due to
OL,12,Ffuel spillage. It is now being re-
OL,13,Fsurfaced and is expected to re-open on
OL,14,FSunday evening.
OL,16,FDiversions are in place
